verse.lines:
{lang-eng}My Savior, Thou hast offered rest:
Oh, give it then to me;
The rest of ceasing from myself,
To find my all in Thee.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}O Lord, I seek a holy rest,
A victory over sin;
I seek that Thou alone shouldst reign
O’er all without, within.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}In Thy strong hand I lay me down,
So shall the work be done;
For who can work so wondrously
As the Almighty One?{/lang-eng}
